---
title: Beef Strips with Ballymaloe Relish served with wedges and tomato salad
description: Rich Ballymaloe tomato relish is a perfect pairing for the juicy beef strips it coats in this recipe. The accompanying potato wedges and simple side salad with Greek style cheese make for a beautifully balanced meal.
